a:5:{s:5:"title";s:58:"Salesmate AI Agents gain meeting reschedule/cancel actions";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:428:"<p>Salesmate added the ability for AI Agents to modify bookings—including rescheduling and canceling—directly within conversations.</p>
<p>Where to find it: AI Agents → Tools → Meeting Scheduler.</p>
<p>Effect: fewer manual scheduling back-and-forth steps.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/">https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/</a></p>
